Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍腐於野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆斷於利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛之人 且赴黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨我可就找錯門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨的話就恨德川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨駿府的家康大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨將軍繼承人之爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 詛咒自己為何生在甲賀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天 終於到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦…之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說聽見打鬥的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在那兒抖什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是朧出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼交待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒有劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿起劍吧 朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不得不置我於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我的雙目被封
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的雙眼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀人幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我自己封住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想目睹與卍谷人的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這雙眼睛重見光明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀只剩我一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀也只剩下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拔劍啊 朧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不殺朧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要背叛甲賀 背叛卍谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人欺騙您 陷害您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鍔隱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快動手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的…安居之所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在於…此世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一個人活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒性…消失…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想…我不想殺任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓任何人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甲賀人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀弦之介來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天膳大人又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫要驚慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳是不死的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是都知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人 扶他起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那顆腦袋給他放回原處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是關係到竹千代少爺 也關係到我阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也關係到你們命運的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 朧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心藥師寺天膳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也許還沒有見過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會不死的秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也非忍術範疇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身體裏寄宿著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道那究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟那傳說早在我出生之前就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有確認之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 依我之見 寄生在他體內的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 說太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對今後路還長的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我也老糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛能看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不太對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就藏在…朧身後…的台階下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對今後路還長的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等甲賀卍谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀鍔隱一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身懷可怕忍法秘術的雙方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以長年宿怨為由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實為愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此認為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對今後路還長的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此認為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…朧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方纔天膳所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 我的身後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺著身受重傷又了中毒的甲賀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死無反抗之力的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有損伊賀之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說什麼話 一點不像忍者的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火速派人報告服部半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快備馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雙方忍眾仲裁的半藏大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可有異議？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…異議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂靜暮春
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然楚楚稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無垢的兩個靈魂墜入藍色冥暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同轉瞬即逝的泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消逝在青藍月輝的他界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏於心的羈絆 飄搖的悲戀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數度輪迴之後再續前緣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越千萬暗夜再結連理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,basilisk 甲賀忍法帖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終話

